<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, September 26 (Xinhua) -- Indian Prime Minister Inder
Kumar Gujral returned home today after winding up a nine-day
three-nation tour which took him to Tanzania, the United States
and Italy.
</P>
<P>
