<HEADLINE> Plane Crashes in Indonesia, All 221 on Board Feared Dead </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, September 26 (Xinhua) -- A Garuda Indonesia Airbus
crashed today in a mountainous region near the city of Medan in
North Sumatra. All 221 people on board are feared dead, police
said.
</P>
