Congress organized by his department, Wang Zhaoguo, Head of the
United Front Work Department of the CPC Central Committee, said
that "the congress has worked out a comprehensive strategy for
China's cross-century reform and opening up and socialist
modernization, and it will have a far-reaching impact on the
United Front work."
</P>
<P>
