out by the congress, reinforce the Party's efforts in
all aspects and rally closely around the Party Central Committee
with Jiang Zemin at the core;
</P>
<P>
-- To support and help non-Party members and United Front
members in their efforts to study the essence of the Party
congress and create good conditions for their studies.
</P>
<P>
Since September 19, the department has presented the main ideas
of the Party congress documents to representatives from
non-Communist parties, people with no party affiliations,
intellectual circles in the capital, religious groups and ethnic
minorities. 
