The four men were earlier all sentenced to life imprisonment
for the murder that took place on April 11, 1996.
</P>
<P>
The assassination happened near Saengchai's home when he and
his wife were driving home after a dinner at a restaurant.
</P>
<P>
It was believed that the motive behind the murder was the
conflict of interest.  
