scored at will from the baseline. He finished with 19
points. While Veteran pivot Panagiotis Fasoulas dominated the
boards with 15 points and 11 rebounds.
</P>
<P>
Olympiakos beat Turkey's Efes Pilsen 70-67 last week in
Istanbul in the opening match of group A. And it is said that CSKA
were facing closure because of financial problems. 
