<HEADLINE> Tour of Spain Cycling Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MADRID, September 25 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results from
the 19th stage of the Tour of Spain, a 184-kilometer race from
Valladolid to Los Angeles de San Rafael on Thursday:
</P>
<P>
1. Jose Maria Jimenez, Spain, Banesto, four hours, 31 minutes,
38 seconds
